{"serial": "77028", "department_serial": 62, "code": "HK4034", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "AI and Writing", "ch": "人工智慧與寫作"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Liao,Chang-Yen"], "ch": ["廖長彥"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "HK", "room": "219"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 40, "department": {"ch": "客家語文暨社會科學學系", "en": "Department of Hakka Language and Social Sciences"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 2, "selected": 31, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程主要目的為介紹各式人工智慧在寫作表達的技術與應用，讓學習者對於人工智慧科技應用於寫作表達有所認識與理解，提供人社領域與非人社領域的學生有機會從案例與實作了解人工智慧對於寫作表達的真實影響。課程內容將介紹AI寫作、AI繪圖、AI新聞、AI問答、AI聊天機器人、AI故事等應用之基本原理、實際操作、作品練習。最後將會以以跨領域小組方式進行專題探索以完成小組專題，深化學生對AI與寫作的理解。\n\n課程目標 \n1、認識與了解人工智慧\n2、認識運用人工智慧在各式創造領域相關工具與環境\n3、掌握基本的人工智慧技巧\n4、能運用人工智慧工具進行寫作專題的小組專題實作", "en": "The main purpose of this course is to introduce various technologies and applications of artificial intelligence in writing expression so that learners can understand and understand the application of artificial intelligence technology in writing presentations and provide students in the field of human society and non-human society with the opportunity And practice to understand the real impact of artificial intelligence on writing expression. The course content will introduce the basic principles, practical operations, and work exercises of AI writing, AI drawing, AI news, AI question and answer, AI chat robot, AI story, and other applications. Finally, the topic will be explored in a cross-disciplinary group to complete the group topic and deepen students' understanding of AI and writing.\n\nCourse targets \n1. Know and understand artificial intelligence\n2. Understand the tools and environment related to the use of artificial intelligence in various creative fields\n3. Master basic artificial intelligence skills\n4. Group projects that can use artificial intelligence tools for writing projects"}, "outline": {"ch": "102/15課程介紹與進度說明\n202/22AI的發展與現況，如openAI\n303/01AI寫作：AI Writer\n403/08AI新聞生產：智搜\n503/15AI問答：Azure OpenAI\n603/22AI聊天機器人：contentbot\n703/29AI故事創作：Wattpad\n804/05清明節，本週停課\n904/12AI繪圖：MidJourney\n1004/19<提案>有關AI創作之資訊收集，需包括：設計主題、設計動機、文獻與相關資訊之檢索\n1104/26其他新興相關議題\n1205/03創意思考啟發活動\n1305/10創意思考啟發活動\n1405/17創意思考啟發活動\n1505/24<期末報告>：AI寫作小組專題\n1605/31期末報告修改", "en": "1 02/15 Course introduction and progress description\n2 02/22 The development and current situation of AI, such as openAI\n3 03/01 AI Writing: AI Writer\n4 03/08 AI News Production: Zhisou\n5 03/15 AI Q&A: Azure OpenAI\n6 03/22 AI chatbot: contentbot\n7 03/29 AI Story Creation: Wattpad\n8 04/05 Tomb-sweeping Day, no classes this week\n9 04/12 AI Drawing: MidJourney\n10 04/19\nInformation collection about AI creation, including design theme, design motivation, literature, and related information retrieval\n11 04/26 Other Emerging Related Issues\n12 05/03 Creative Thinking Inspirational Activities\n13 05/10 Creative Thinking Inspirational Activities\n14 05/17 Creative Thinking Inspirational Activities\n15 05/24\n: AI writing group topic\n16 05/31 Revision of the final report"}, "textbook": {"ch": "自編教材", "en": "self-made teaching materials"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100", "en": "100"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n實習/實驗", "en": ["Lecture", "", "Practical Training Lab"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1.出席與課堂參與活動：25%\n2.小組案例討論：25%\n3.小組專題 50%", "en": "1. Attendance and class participation activities: 25%\n2. Group case discussion: 25%\n3. Group project 50%"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週三12:00-13:00", "en": "Wednesday 12:00-13:00"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "AI應用調查", "en": "Survey of AI Applications"}, "domain": {"ch": "語言與文學領域", "en": "語言與文學領域"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "具備客家語言文化的基本能力", "rating": "(0)無", "assesments": ["無"]}, {"compet